<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="am">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>የግዢ ውጤት</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 100px; }
        .box { border: 2px solid green; display: inline-block; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; }
        h1 { color: green; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <h1>እንኳን ደስ አሎት!</h1>
        <p>ውድ <strong><%= name %></strong>፣ የሎተሪ ቁጥርዎ፡</p>
        <h2 style="background: yellow; padding: 10px;"><%= ticketNumber %></h2>
        <a href="/">ተመለስ</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
